WEBVTT

00:00:06.846 --> 00:00:09.694
MISSUS FANIA FAINER, TAPE NUMBER THREE,

00:00:09.694 --> 00:00:12.357
AUGUST TWENTY FIFTH, NINETEEN NINETY FIVE.

00:00:13.005 --> 00:00:15.800
MISSUS Fayner, ir hot geredt vegn selektsye.

00:00:15.823 --> 00:00:16.773
YES.

00:00:16.773 --> 00:00:19.934
di selektsye hob ikh probirt oyfklern vos es heyst.

00:00:19.958 --> 00:00:24.322
me nemt dir, me tut dir oys naket un me makht dir rekhts un links.

00:00:24.430 --> 00:00:29.649
dan ven zey filn az zey hobn tsu fil mentshn ze-, hobn zey gevolt likvidirn, iz geven dos,

00:00:29.649 --> 00:00:33.266
m'hot gemakht mamesh khoyzek fun dir, m'hot dir geheysn aroysshteln dem tsung.

00:00:33.812 --> 00:00:38.193
un mir zaynen geven naket un undzere zakhn hobn mir gegat oyfn ha- oyfn hant.

00:00:39.617 --> 00:00:40.522
ven m'hot,

00:00:40.528 --> 00:00:49.668
dan iz geven a groyse selektsye. m'hot tsugenumen kimat fun ts- fun toyznter hot men ibergelozn etlekhe hundert meydlekh. ale zaynen gegangen in gaz-oyvns.

00:00:50.012 --> 00:00:51.946
haynt, m'hot opgeshribn dem numer.

00:00:52.307 --> 00:00:53.938
un geyendik azoy

00:00:54.298 --> 00:00:57.493
hot mir eyn meydl gegebn aza shtarkn patsh,

00:00:57.493 --> 00:00:59.070
a meydl vos iz gezesn,

00:00:59.310 --> 00:00:59.631
a...

00:01:00.036 --> 00:01:04.282
dos zaynen geven meydlekh vos zaynen shoyn geven fun frier in di lagern,

00:01:04.962 --> 00:01:09.024
un zey hobn shoyn farnumen amt, in di OFFICES, zey hobn gearbet mit di daytshn.

00:01:11.292 --> 00:01:13.853
hot eyne fun zey hot mir gegebn dem patsh.

00:01:13.853 --> 00:01:16.499
un ikh hob geshtanen un ikh hob getrakht,

00:01:17.130 --> 00:01:20.904
far vos hot zi mir gegebn a patsh? nisht genug vos di daytshn

00:01:21.720 --> 00:01:27.842
patshn un shlogn un shisn, vi kumt a yidishe tokhter zol mir gebn a patsh? far vos? un ikh bin gegangen vayter,

00:01:27.842 --> 00:01:33.155
ven zi hot mir gegebn dem patsh hot zi mir gegebn a zog, "nem di zakhn oyf der anderer zayt fun dayn hant."

00:01:34.090 --> 00:01:35.704
aroysgeyendik

00:01:36.418 --> 00:01:40.631
hot zi gehat genug seykhl tsu farshteyn az ikh'l trakhtn vegn dem,

00:01:40.654 --> 00:01:42.347
iz zi mir nokhgelofn.

00:01:42.347 --> 00:01:43.905
zi hot mir gezogt,

00:01:44.198 --> 00:01:48.343
"ikh hob gevolt zolst lebn. ikh hob gevolt farshteln dayn numer,

00:01:48.467 --> 00:01:51.059
az keyner zol dos nisht kenen aropshraybn,

00:01:51.370 --> 00:01:53.712
vayl," zogt zi, "es geshet zeyer oft

00:01:53.712 --> 00:01:55.678
ven es kumt for a selektsye,

00:01:55.678 --> 00:02:00.453
un az me nemt bay imetsn avek a mamen, oder me nemt avek a kuzin oder a shvester,

00:02:00.453 --> 00:02:02.158
khapt zi an ander numer

00:02:02.158 --> 00:02:06.567
un shpeter nemt der daytsh dem andern numer. ikh hob gevolt," zogt zi, "zolst lebn."

00:02:06.895 --> 00:02:08.115
du farshteyst?

00:02:08.115 --> 00:02:10.072
dos zaynen geven meydlekh

00:02:10.072 --> 00:02:13.858
vos hobn gehat yoysher a bisl, un zaynen geven

00:02:14.218 --> 00:02:18.852
mentshn vos hobn gezorgt far imetsn andersh oykh, nisht bloyz far zikh aleyn.

00:02:19.078 --> 00:02:22.413
un azelkhe mentshn hob ikh bagegnt in yenem gehenem,

00:02:22.538 --> 00:02:25.243
vu m'hot gebrent un geharget

00:02:25.243 --> 00:02:28.033
un m'hot nisht, eyne fun andere hot geganvet,

00:02:28.107 --> 00:02:31.628
un in a gevise mos hot der daytsh dergreykht

00:02:32.629 --> 00:02:33.720
vos er hot

00:02:33.777 --> 00:02:37.621
der pr- farn prayz fun lebn hobn mentshn geton shreklekhe zakhn,

00:02:37.621 --> 00:02:39.221
kedey tsu lebn nokh a tog.

00:02:39.312 --> 00:02:42.478
dem numer hostu nokh oyf dayn orem, yo?

00:02:41.573 --> 00:02:42.450
YES.

00:02:42.580 --> 00:02:45.170
ikh volt gebetn zolst oyfheybn dayn orem,

00:02:45.170 --> 00:02:46.309
un vayzn.

00:02:46.028 --> 00:02:47.678
mayn numer iz

00:02:47.678 --> 00:02:49.312
tsvey fir

00:02:49.352 --> 00:02:51.236
zibn zero f-

00:02:51.445 --> 00:02:54.010
zibn fir tsvey nul zibn.

00:02:51.720 --> 00:02:52.570
zibn.

00:02:54.020 --> 00:02:54.520
YES.

00:02:54.988 --> 00:02:57.800
du zest beser far mir, YES, IT IS.

00:03:01.907 --> 00:03:02.354
OKAY.

00:03:02.683 --> 00:03:06.085
hostu gevolt a a mol oysmekn dem numer?

00:03:05.164 --> 00:03:06.089
NO.

00:03:06.089 --> 00:03:08.567
ikh hob nisht geton keyn shlekhts in mayn lebn.

00:03:08.623 --> 00:03:11.857
dos iz zoln zikh, zoln zikh shemen di daytshn, nisht ikh.

00:03:12.083 --> 00:03:15.874
zey hobn es geton far mir. keyn mol nisht gevolt aropnemen dem numer.

00:03:17.365 --> 00:03:23.147
es iz efsher shver far mentshn tsu farshteyn di badingungen in AUSCHWITZ. iz zog mir vayter,

00:03:23.322 --> 00:03:28.581
vegn, du host shoyn gezogt az dayn siluet hostu, dayn karikatur hostu nisht derkent.

00:03:28.140 --> 00:03:29.760
ABSOLUTELY NOT.

00:03:28.873 --> 00:03:30.436
vegn esn,

00:03:30.338 --> 00:03:31.436
vegn esn iz nish-

00:03:30.662 --> 00:03:32.850
vegn di baderfenishn.

00:03:31.960 --> 00:03:37.025
-nishn. OKAY, ikh vel dir probirn zikh in mayne eygene verter oyfklern vos dortn iz geven.

00:03:37.800 --> 00:03:41.658
ikh hob dir gezogt az s'iz geven a ape- a apel. dos iz geven in der fri.

00:03:42.930 --> 00:03:44.192
flegn mir

00:03:44.192 --> 00:03:46.501
dortn zikh oyfshteln fir a zeyger,

00:03:46.592 --> 00:03:55.263
un dos iz geven dir tsu paynikn, vayle di zelbe zakh hobn zey gekent ton zeks a zeyger, ober zey hobn undz genumen fir a zeyger. mir zaynen geshtanen oyfn gas far tsvey sho, dray sho a mol,

00:03:55.263 --> 00:03:57.487
vi iz di daytshn hot zikh geglust,

00:03:57.595 --> 00:04:00.862
un m'hot oysgerufn dayn numer, m'hot kontrolirt dayn numer,

00:04:00.987 --> 00:04:02.618
un az imetser iz t-,

00:04:03.366 --> 00:04:04.957
imetser hot gefelt,

00:04:04.957 --> 00:04:06.970
hostu gekent shteyn a gantsn tog.

00:04:06.977 --> 00:04:10.768
un s'iz geshen azelkhe faln, vayl fun dem gehenem zaynen mentshn antlofn.

00:04:11.398 --> 00:04:13.164
un glaykhtsaytik,

00:04:13.525 --> 00:04:16.657
iz, ale vos zaynen gekumen dortn,

00:04:18.233 --> 00:04:21.045
vey-, froyen hobn menstruatsye, vegn dem veystu.

00:04:21.863 --> 00:04:22.714
iz,

00:04:23.529 --> 00:04:28.639
hot men zey gegebn kave, un in di kave hot men arayngeton aza meditsin vos es hot gegeysn BRUM,

00:04:30.045 --> 00:04:31.299
un kedey

00:04:31.299 --> 00:04:32.706
nisht tsum,

00:04:32.813 --> 00:04:34.882
az me zol nisht krign, me zol farlirn.

00:04:37.690 --> 00:04:38.935
un dan

00:04:38.935 --> 00:04:42.960
hobn di froyen ge-, der grester teyl, gekrign geshvolene baykher azelkhe.

00:04:42.960 --> 00:04:45.120
m'hot oysgezen take vi karikaturn.

00:04:45.120 --> 00:04:49.209
un mit dem, krigndik di meditsin tsu farlirn di menstruatsye,

00:04:49.435 --> 00:04:53.766
hot men glaykhtsaytik gekrign a durkhfal, dos heyst, men iz gelofn.

00:04:53.856 --> 00:04:55.616
dos iz geven nisht natirlekh.

00:04:55.616 --> 00:05:03.570
un meydlekh hobn gevolt zayn bay der APPEAL, flegt men shteyn, un zay mir moykhl, s'hot gegosn fun zey. zey zaynen geshtanen un bay di fis hot gerunen iber zey.

00:05:03.593 --> 00:05:08.227
un dos iz geven, dos iz geven shreklekh. un mit dem zaynen zeyer a sakh mentshn umgekumen.

00:05:09.921 --> 00:05:15.095
tsum bayshpil, di vos, s'iz geven azoy shtark der durkhfal, vi dos hot gegeysn,

00:05:16.114 --> 00:05:22.523
az meydlekh zaynen geblibn lign in dem ts-, nisht nisht aroysgegangen shoyn tsum apel, vayl zey hobn nisht gekent,

00:05:22.523 --> 00:05:24.691
un m'iz gekumen, m'hot zey genumen in gaz-oyvn.

00:05:24.691 --> 00:05:25.316
farshtey-?

00:05:25.316 --> 00:05:31.700
iz mm ale hobn gevolt geyn tsum apel, afile az s'hot gelofn iber di fis un s'hot, az zey hobn nisht gekent shteyn.

00:05:31.842 --> 00:05:39.818
ober azoy iz es geven. flegt men undz haltn dortn bay dem apel, un ikh, du host gekukt oyf di meydlekh un du host gefregt, vemen vet, ve- vemen vet es geshen morgn?

00:05:39.975 --> 00:05:43.310
ober der daytsh hot geton ale mitlen in der velt

00:05:43.317 --> 00:05:45.218
tsu makhn dir oys mentsh.

00:05:46.270 --> 00:05:48.386
du host gezen mit di eygene oygn

00:05:48.410 --> 00:05:48.740
ye?

00:05:48.650 --> 00:05:50.651
az froyen zenen arayn in gaz-oyvn?

00:05:50.640 --> 00:05:51.815
frayvilik?

00:05:51.822 --> 00:05:53.472
ye, vos far a frage?

00:05:53.472 --> 00:05:59.522
zey hobn zikh, s'iz gekumen tsu aza moment ven meydlekh flegn zikh onheybn bashlisn bay zikh, kumen fun a tog arbet,

00:05:59.522 --> 00:06:01.299
un bashlisn az zey hobn genug.

00:06:01.626 --> 00:06:05.147
flegn, mir zaynen geven arumgeringlt mit elektrishe drotn,

00:06:06.790 --> 00:06:08.657
flegt men kumen tsu geyn

00:06:09.507 --> 00:06:15.221
un zey hobn opgeredt tsvishn zikh az morgn geyen zey t- aleyn tsu di elektrishe drotn.

00:06:15.261 --> 00:06:20.236
zaynen zey, finf meydlekh, zeks meydlekh, zikh nemen far di hent un tsugeyn tsu di elektrishe drotn,

00:06:20.236 --> 00:06:22.072
un onrirn di drotn,

00:06:22.112 --> 00:06:26.628
un oyfn ort vern elektrizirt un NACH dem iz arayngevorfn in krematoryum tsu farbrenen.

00:06:26.905 --> 00:06:31.843
ober azelkhe zakhn iz geven tog-teglekh. tog-teglekh azelkhe zakhn ven ikh bin gekumen.

00:06:31.950 --> 00:06:34.593
un ven ikh hob gezen d- vi me firt in gaz-oyvn,

00:06:34.633 --> 00:06:37.853
di meydlekh vos bay der selektsye hot men opgeshribn

00:06:37.853 --> 00:06:39.470
dem numer,

00:06:40.928 --> 00:06:42.154
hot men

00:06:43.763 --> 00:06:47.227
hot men shpe- oyf morgn oder shpeter bay nakht, far nakht,

00:06:47.227 --> 00:06:48.350
gekumen mit

00:06:49.476 --> 00:06:50.390
TRUCKS,

00:06:50.390 --> 00:06:54.793
dos heyst, s'iz geven TOWAROWE&lt;varg&gt;, un m'hot zey ale arayngeshtelt,

00:06:54.867 --> 00:06:59.923
un mir hobn zey ale gezen un dan, mir hobn zikh gezegnt mit zey. mir hobn gevust vu zey geyen, un der gaz-oyvn,

00:07:00.013 --> 00:07:01.984
der gaz-oyvn hot gebrent,

00:07:01.984 --> 00:07:05.103
di krematoryum faktish, vos m'hot gebrent di kerpers,

00:07:05.650 --> 00:07:07.500
fir un tsvantsik sho.

00:07:08.046 --> 00:07:10.588
un zay mir moykhl ven ikh vel dir zogn

00:07:11.505 --> 00:07:14.334
az ven bist arayn in AUSCHWITZ vu ikh bin geven

00:07:14.627 --> 00:07:15.701
hot azoy

00:07:15.775 --> 00:07:21.146
geshtunken, azoy gefilt mentshlekhe, mentshlekhe, vos m'hot gebrent mentshlekhe kerpers,

00:07:21.146 --> 00:07:24.358
az du shtelst zikh gornisht for. dos iz geven nisht tsu bashraybn.

00:07:24.415 --> 00:07:27.261
der geshtank vos s'iz geven fun brenen mentshn.

00:07:27.823 --> 00:07:31.895
ki-, vayle ven ikh bin gekumen, ikh bin gekumen frier, iz nokh nisht geven der,

00:07:31.895 --> 00:07:33.740
flegn zey in b- in griber,

00:07:34.067 --> 00:07:37.689
derhargenen, dershisn, un in griber, un shpeter iz ge- hobn zey ge-

00:07:37.729 --> 00:07:40.642
gehat etlekhe krematoryums gemakht in AUSCHWITZ.

00:07:40.902 --> 00:07:42.904
frier iz geven bloyz in

00:07:44.749 --> 00:07:49.164
BI- BIRKENAU iz geven der lager un der krematoryum iz geven in AUSCHWITZ.

00:07:50.976 --> 00:07:52.421
vu hot ir geshlofn?

00:07:52.461 --> 00:07:56.404
mir hobn geshlofn, s'iz geven azelkhe gemakht hiltserne

00:07:56.697 --> 00:07:59.171
palates, azelkhe gor groyse,

00:07:59.785 --> 00:08:01.061
un s'iz geven

00:08:01.540 --> 00:08:05.620
avekgeleygt, s'iz nisht geven keyn shtroy, s'iz nisht geven keyn zakh, oyf der &lt;kh-&gt;, oyf der...

00:08:05.620 --> 00:08:10.747
azelkhe finef, t- NO, mir zaynen geven zeks meydlekh in a, aza min KOJe.

00:08:11.007 --> 00:08:14.106
iz geven eyne, tsvey, dray azelkhe KOJes,

00:08:14.365 --> 00:08:22.864
un in der KOJe hobn mir geshlofn zeks meydlekh. mir zaynen geven di ale vos zaynen gekumen mit mir tsuzamen fun Lomzher turme, hobn mir azoy geshlofn tsuzamen, zeks meydlekh.

00:08:23.190 --> 00:08:26.289
ken ikh fregn vayter vegn Lomzher turme?

00:08:24.253 --> 00:08:24.770
bite.

00:08:25.755 --> 00:08:26.559
ye.

00:08:26.599 --> 00:08:29.107
Lomzher turme iz geven

00:08:29.957 --> 00:08:31.498
oyf azoy vayt,

00:08:31.498 --> 00:08:33.039
dos iz geven a tfise.

00:08:33.400 --> 00:08:35.453
un s'iz geven merstn teyl

00:08:35.965 --> 00:08:40.855
di, in di tsimern, mir zaynen geven arumgeringlt mit azelkhe ayzerne drotn,

00:08:40.855 --> 00:08:46.657
mit azelkhe ayzerne tirn, az voltst gemeynt az dos zaynen di greste farbrekher in der velt.

00:08:47.153 --> 00:08:48.750
azoy hot dos oysgezen.

00:08:49.026 --> 00:08:53.629
iz inem tsimer vos normal zitst eyn, eyn arestant in a tsimer,

00:08:53.629 --> 00:08:55.837
hot men undz arayngevorfn akht meydlekh.

00:08:56.147 --> 00:09:00.309
zaynen mir shteyendik mamesh geshlofn, shteyendik, vayl s'iz nisht geven keyn betn.

00:09:00.484 --> 00:09:03.797
m'hot zikh avekgezetst oyf dr'erd eyne oyf di andere un azoy iz men geshlofn.

00:09:03.797 --> 00:09:07.700
mir hobn gekrign vaser. mir hobn gekrign a portsye broyt,

00:09:07.707 --> 00:09:10.316
un nokh a mol, s'iz geshtanen a emer.

00:09:11.267 --> 00:09:15.280
un in dem emer hostu dayne ale baderfenishn, vayl m'hot dir nit aroysgelozn.

00:09:15.280 --> 00:09:16.577
un in der fri

00:09:16.684 --> 00:09:18.385
flegt kumen der

00:09:18.385 --> 00:09:21.844
der vekhter vos hot undz opgehit, dos iz geven a daytsh,

00:09:21.844 --> 00:09:23.158
oder a polyak,

00:09:23.502 --> 00:09:25.439
un er hot dir geheysn aroystrogn

00:09:25.439 --> 00:09:29.908
dem emer mit di ale zakhn vos iz dortn un ot azoy iz es geven.

00:09:29.998 --> 00:09:32.742
azoy ho'mir gelebt a lon- a lange tsayt.

00:09:33.188 --> 00:09:40.792
mir, in Lomzher turme bin ikh keyn mol nisht gegangen tsu keyn arbet un keyner iz nisht gegangen tsu keyn arbet, &lt;zaynen mir&gt; dortn biz vanent mir zaynen avek in Shtuthof.

00:09:41.220 --> 00:09:49.584
hostu a mol gehert oge- oder gezen, oder in Lomzhe oder in in AUSCHWITZ, az a daytsh zol a mol tsutshepen tsu a froy?

00:09:46.217 --> 00:09:47.225
ye, ye?

00:09:50.637 --> 00:09:55.434
ikh hob es perzenlekh nisht gezen. ober ikh hob gegert vegn dem. ikh hob gegert vegn dem.

00:09:55.434 --> 00:09:58.021
ober AUSCHWITZ hot gegat aza min zakh,

00:10:00.424 --> 00:10:02.851
okh! dos iz shver tsu redn vegn dem.

00:10:02.851 --> 00:10:04.460
er hot gegat a blok,

00:10:05.082 --> 00:10:06.780
fun eksperimentn.

00:10:07.883 --> 00:10:09.685
vu m'hot arayngenumen froyen,

00:10:09.685 --> 00:10:13.159
m'hot arayngenumen tsvilingen, m'hot arayngenumen kinder,

00:10:13.755 --> 00:10:20.414
un zey hobn gemakht oyf zey eksperimentn. un zey hobn arayngenumen meydlekh yunge vos iz zey gefeln gevorn. s'iz geven a Mengele,

00:10:20.809 --> 00:10:26.253
un ven mir hobn im gezen bay a selektsye, ven mir hobn im gezen, er hot geshtanen bar APPEAL,

00:10:26.277 --> 00:10:28.667
hot yeder eyner geshtorbn ineveynik.

00:10:28.318 --> 00:10:29.730
ir hot gezen Mengele?

00:10:29.670 --> 00:10:36.008
okh! er iz geshtanen lebn undz! keseyder lebn mir, ye. er iz geven a a prakht fun a man, a militer-man,

00:10:36.604 --> 00:10:40.040
un Mengele iz geven der vos hot oysgeklibn.

00:10:40.468 --> 00:10:43.249
dos iz geven a merder in vayse hentshkes.

00:10:43.249 --> 00:10:46.858
s'iz zikh shver fortsushteln vos der mentsh hot mit zikh forgeshtelt.

00:10:47.117 --> 00:10:51.093
er hot oysgeklibn mentshn farn, dem eksperimentn-blok.

00:10:52.078 --> 00:10:54.468
un ikh bin keyn mol dortn nisht geven.

00:10:55.420 --> 00:10:57.186
ikh veys nor eyn zakh:

00:10:57.360 --> 00:10:59.559
kh'hob bagegnt nokh der milkhome

00:10:59.559 --> 00:11:01.049
eyne fun a tsviling.

00:11:01.950 --> 00:11:03.800
hot zi mir gezogt azoy:

00:11:04.549 --> 00:11:08.525
vos dortn iz forgekumen! m'hot aroysgeshnitn KIDNEYS,

00:11:08.869 --> 00:11:10.922
fu- eyne fun andern, di nirn,

00:11:10.928 --> 00:11:12.508
eyne fun tsveytn,

00:11:12.970 --> 00:11:19.092
men hot geton azelkhe groyzame, m'hot, oyb, m'hot, -makht meditsinish shvere eksperimentn, un glaykhtsaytik,

00:11:19.092 --> 00:11:23.020
froyen hobn zey gehat prekhtike froyen velkhe zey hobn genitst ven zey hobn gevolt.

00:11:24.158 --> 00:11:29.029
mener hobn zey kastrirt, oykh oysgeklibn di shenste mener vos iz geven un zey hobn es kastrirt.

00:11:29.035 --> 00:11:30.339
froyen hobn zey...

00:11:30.339 --> 00:11:34.766
ober ikh perzenlekh bin keyn mol nisht geven. ikh hob zikh dervust vegn dem.

00:11:38.130 --> 00:11:42.708
AUSCHWITZ iz geven a meshugoim-hoyz. s'iz shver zikh fortsushteln vos dos iz geven.

00:11:42.708 --> 00:11:46.173
ven ir zaynt arayn in der fri, ven m'hot aykh gefirt tsu der arbet,

00:11:46.348 --> 00:11:48.147
iz geshtanen a orkester,

00:11:48.593 --> 00:11:51.366
fun di beste muziker vos iz geven in EUROPE,

00:11:51.366 --> 00:11:55.067
hobn zey oysgeklibn un m'hot aykh geshpilt MUSIC.

00:11:55.090 --> 00:11:57.845
men hot gemakht dortn a khor, di vos kenen zingen

00:11:57.845 --> 00:11:59.099
hobn gezungen.

00:11:59.258 --> 00:12:09.191
vi kenen zikh mentshn forshteln? do zaynen geven gru- grubn in velkhe m'hot gebrent lebedike mentshn, un do shteyt a orkester un shpilt, me shpilt ot tsu ts- barn aroysgeyn tsu der arbet.

00:12:09.788 --> 00:12:12.229
ober s'iz geven a meshugoim-hoyz,

00:12:12.336 --> 00:12:14.743
un ikh vil dir zogn,

00:12:15.610 --> 00:12:19.283
der p- dos lebn hot in zikh aza min koyekh,

00:12:19.390 --> 00:12:23.383
az ikh hob gehat dem gefil yeder eyner vil lebn, keyner vil nit geyn in gaz-oyvn.

00:12:23.625 --> 00:12:28.310
un tsi andere hobn es geton oyfn kheshbn fun andere? s'iz geven azelkhe.

00:12:28.992 --> 00:12:31.753
ober der grester teyl fun di mentshn

00:12:34.071 --> 00:12:38.402
zaynen geven mentshn, zaynen geblibn mentshn, zaynen nisht geven keyn khayes.

00:12:38.695 --> 00:12:44.072
ikh hob gegat taynes tsu mentshn, ikh veys, di vos hobn gegarbet, s'iz geven a zonder-komande.

00:12:44.922 --> 00:12:47.447
di zonder-komande iz bashtanen fun mener

00:12:47.503 --> 00:12:48.695
un froyen,

00:12:50.406 --> 00:12:54.298
velkhe hobn dir tsugenumen di zakhn ven du bist gekumen tsu geyn,

00:12:54.422 --> 00:12:56.452
velkhe hobn geven di vos hobn

00:12:56.452 --> 00:12:59.530
geholfn gazeven, vos zaynen geven di vos hobn

00:13:00.262 --> 00:13:01.412
farbrent.

00:13:01.628 --> 00:13:03.866
hob ikh gehat shreklekhe taynes.

00:13:04.817 --> 00:13:10.514
ober ven ikh hob geredt tsu zikh aleyn: vos volt ikh geton ven a daytsh klaybt mir oys

00:13:10.622 --> 00:13:12.776
tsu arbetn bar aza min arbet?

00:13:12.833 --> 00:13:15.428
tsi ikh volt gegat dem koyekh

00:13:15.428 --> 00:13:17.451
araynvarfn zikh in grub aleyn?

00:13:17.575 --> 00:13:20.336
tsi ikh volt geton vos der daytsh...? azoyernokh

00:13:20.595 --> 00:13:26.664
zayendik yung hob ikh, ikh hob gemishpet di mentshn, ikh hob gehat taynes tsu zey far vos zey tuen es.

00:13:27.818 --> 00:13:31.232
ober ven ikh bin gevorn elter hob ikh geredt tsu zikh un ikh hob getrakht,

00:13:31.232 --> 00:13:34.848
du veyst nisht vi du voltst gehandlt vi a mentsh,

00:13:34.990 --> 00:13:38.342
ven me kumt un me shtelt dir tsu dem revolver tsum kop.

00:13:39.546 --> 00:13:44.116
farshteyst? far derfar zog ikh az AUSCHWITZ iz geven a shreklekhe zakh, shreklekh tsu lebn,

00:13:44.116 --> 00:13:45.609
un shreklekh tsu zayn,

00:13:45.609 --> 00:13:48.297
un shreklekh tsu zayn a eydes fun dem alemen.

00:13:48.321 --> 00:13:51.302
ober s'iz geven dortn momentn ven mames

00:13:51.460 --> 00:13:55.318
farn prayz fun veln lebn nokh a tog avekgevorfn zeyere kinder.

00:13:56.168 --> 00:13:59.469
farshteyst? kinder hobn geganvet di broyt bay der mamen.

00:14:00.522 --> 00:14:04.431
dos iz zakhn vos iz, a normaler mentsh, a mentsh vos trakht,

00:14:04.622 --> 00:14:06.404
ken zikh es nisht forshteln.

00:14:06.867 --> 00:14:09.411
vayle mames zaynen di vos zaynen greyt

00:14:09.411 --> 00:14:11.771
avektsugebn zeyer lebn far a kind,

00:14:11.878 --> 00:14:13.779
ober do vi zi iz geshtanen

00:14:13.836 --> 00:14:17.019
un zi hot gevust az mitn kind geyt zi glaykh in gaz-oyvn,

00:14:17.616 --> 00:14:21.390
hot zi oyf aza min oyfn zikh gevolt rateven, hot zi avekgevorfn ir kind.

00:14:23.674 --> 00:14:27.566
shver, shver iz tsu mishpetn, shver, zeyer shver iz tsu

00:14:28.365 --> 00:14:32.763
zogn, zey zaynen geven umgerekht, un ikh bin gerekht, yo un ikh veys nit.

00:14:33.411 --> 00:14:37.185
vayl ikh hob eyn eyntsik mol, tsu mir arayngekumen a bokher,

00:14:37.815 --> 00:14:41.943
dos iz geven glaykh vi ikh hob zikh umgekert nokh der milkhome keyn Byalistok,

00:14:43.249 --> 00:14:44.863
un ikh hob im gefregt,

00:14:46.641 --> 00:14:52.847
"vos hostu geton in AUSCHWITZ?" hot er mir gezogt, er hot gornit, er hot gefilt az er iz gornit shuldik,

00:14:52.847 --> 00:14:57.705
zogt er, er hot gegarbet in der zonder-komande. hob ikh geefnt di tir, ikh hob im aroysgetribn.

00:14:57.930 --> 00:15:02.109
shpeter hob ikh geredt tsu zikh, ver bin ikh tsu bashuldikn?

00:15:03.617 --> 00:15:07.138
er iz a mentsh, er hot zikh geratevet. mayn mazl iz geven

00:15:07.144 --> 00:15:08.522
vos ikh hob

00:15:09.405 --> 00:15:12.571
gearbet, m'hot mir arayngefirt un ikh hob gearbet in a fabrik.

00:15:12.949 --> 00:15:14.777
im, dos iz geven zayn fabrik!

00:15:14.777 --> 00:15:16.453
farshteyst? azoyernokh az ikh,

00:15:16.560 --> 00:15:18.832
s'iz ersht fuftsik yor nokh dem,

00:15:18.838 --> 00:15:20.523
un ikh trakht nokh alts

00:15:20.523 --> 00:15:23.625
az keyner, nisht keyner, n-, ikh oykh nisht,

00:15:24.778 --> 00:15:29.366
kenen bashuldikn di mentshn vos hobn gegarbet dortn bay di un andere zakhn,

00:15:29.366 --> 00:15:35.077
vos iz nisht geven, loyt mayn, dos, nisht geven rikhtik, un nisht fayn un nisht gut un nisht mentshlekh, BUT,

00:15:35.077 --> 00:15:36.416
der prayz fun lebn,

00:15:36.416 --> 00:15:37.820
shtarker fun undz.

00:15:40.450 --> 00:15:42.981
vos hot dir gegebn mut vayter tsu geyn?

00:15:43.712 --> 00:15:45.194
ikh veys nit. di,

00:15:45.194 --> 00:15:46.527
kh'hob gevolt lebn.

00:15:46.527 --> 00:15:50.455
ikh hob gega- ikh, zogndik frier hob ikh geredt vegn mayn bruder.

00:15:50.884 --> 00:15:53.139
fleg ikh lign oyf der KOJe un zogn azoy.

00:15:53.280 --> 00:15:57.746
efsher tate-mame zaynen eltere far undz, zey veln umkumen.

00:15:58.309 --> 00:16:04.499
ober mayn shvesterke iz yinger far undz, zi iz geven tsen yor, efsher vet zi, ober mayn bruder vet dokh blaybn, oybe ikh vel blaybn lebn,

00:16:04.499 --> 00:16:06.743
vet er blaybn, un er vet mir darfn hobn.

00:16:06.743 --> 00:16:11.280
Leybl vet blaybn lebn, un az Leybl vet blaybn lebn darf ikh zayn mit im.

00:16:11.995 --> 00:16:13.713
un glaykhtsaytik,

00:16:13.713 --> 00:16:19.228
vest nisht gloybn, s'iz shver far mentshn zikh forshteln, az mir ze- flegn kumen fun a tog arbet,

00:16:19.538 --> 00:16:22.856
un krign dortn di bisl yushke hot dos gegeysn, di bisl zup,

00:16:23.014 --> 00:16:27.581
flegt men zitsn oyf der KOJe, un dos iz geven noente meydlekh vos zaynen geven mit mir,

00:16:27.756 --> 00:16:29.285
un me flegt zingen,

00:16:30.692 --> 00:16:31.875
zingen

00:16:33.855 --> 00:16:35.450
farsheydene lider.

00:16:36.075 --> 00:16:39.540
un m'hot zikh gemutikt eyne dem andern. dos hot gegolfn.

00:16:39.540 --> 00:16:42.392
farshteyst? un take di Rutke r-, un vegn bikher,

00:16:42.392 --> 00:16:44.763
vayl ikh hob geleyent dentsmol zeyer vintsik,

00:16:44.763 --> 00:16:46.486
hern, un dertseylungen,

00:16:46.486 --> 00:16:50.331
zaynen geven zeyer vikhtike zakhn far mir. azoyernokh az, dos mistam hot...

00:16:50.841 --> 00:16:53.200
un keyn held bin ikh keyn mol nisht geven,

00:16:53.200 --> 00:16:56.035
keyn mol nit, ikh hob zikh keyn mol nisht geshtupt,

00:16:56.035 --> 00:17:00.572
vayzt oys, tsi du gloybst ye tsi du gloybst nit, der goyrl iz geven aza

00:17:00.949 --> 00:17:04.422
az ven m'hot likvidirt AUSCHWITZ dem nayntsetn yanuar,

00:17:04.422 --> 00:17:06.561
in nayntsn finef un fertsik,

00:17:07.058 --> 00:17:10.629
iz geven a toytn-marsh. ikh veys nit tsi du host gegert vegn dem.

00:17:11.366 --> 00:17:13.160
der toytn-marsh

00:17:15.022 --> 00:17:17.610
iz oykh geven a shreklekher gehenem.

00:17:17.610 --> 00:17:19.269
men hot undz aroysgefirt,

00:17:19.494 --> 00:17:23.318
zey hobn dan nisht gemakht keyn selektsye, toyznter un toyznter.

00:17:23.426 --> 00:17:25.276
di daytshn zaynen shoyn antlofn.

00:17:25.502 --> 00:17:26.739
hobn zey gevolt,

00:17:26.739 --> 00:17:29.074
ikh veys nit tsi zey hobn moyre gehat far simonim,

00:17:29.080 --> 00:17:32.779
tsi zey hobn gevolt vos aroysnemen di mentshn, ikh veys nit der tsil fun dem,

00:17:32.779 --> 00:17:34.751
ober zey hobn undz alemen gefirt in veg,

00:17:34.751 --> 00:17:37.940
un oyfn veg hobn zey geshpilt, geshpilt mit undz rulet:

00:17:37.940 --> 00:17:42.590
zey hobn gegangen, geshosn, rekhts un links, rekhts un links. s'iz gevorn bay zey a shpil.

00:17:43.592 --> 00:17:48.820
dray monatn hot men ge- mamesh, s'iz geven a gehenem di dray monatn,

00:17:48.820 --> 00:17:53.104
vayle fun toyznter zaynen geblibn zibn tsu akht hundert meydlekh,

00:17:53.380 --> 00:17:58.700
un ikh bin geven tsvishn di. far vos ikh hob nisht gekrign dem koyl veys ikh nit, far vos ikh bin geblibn lebn veys ikh nit.

00:17:58.700 --> 00:18:02.620
ober der fakt iz, m'hot gelofn bin ikh gelofn, m'iz gegangen bin ikh gelofn.

00:18:02.863 --> 00:18:04.477
un dos iz es geven.

00:18:06.542 --> 00:18:07.734
farshteyst?

00:18:08.854 --> 00:18:12.324
AUSCHWITZ, vi lang ikh vel lebn vel ikh es gedenken.

00:18:13.326 --> 00:18:16.847
dos iz a shreklekhe, a sh- shreklekhe tsayt in m-,

00:18:17.106 --> 00:18:21.504
bar a normaln mentsh tsu bagrayfn vos dortn iz forgekumen, s'iz geven shreklekh,

00:18:21.797 --> 00:18:23.445
di ale tsores.

00:18:23.974 --> 00:18:27.253
un der toytn-marsh vet oykh blaybn mit mir,

00:18:27.253 --> 00:18:32.678
vayl dan zaynen umgekumen azoy fil yunge mentshn vos zey hobn shoyn gegat durkhgemakht tsvey yor AUSCHWITZ.

00:18:32.678 --> 00:18:36.771
un in AUSCHWITZ tsu zayn tsvey yor, mentshn hobn keyn tog dortn, keyn tsvey teg,

00:18:36.771 --> 00:18:39.226
un d- oyfn veg zaynen zey umgekumen.

00:18:39.226 --> 00:18:43.509
un men hot mir gefirt fun eyn lager in tsveytn mit dray monatn.

00:18:43.684 --> 00:18:46.344
un ikh hob gehat aza komishn epizod,

00:18:46.806 --> 00:18:50.127
ven m'hot undz gefirt hobn zey undz nisht gegebn keyn esn, di daytshn.

00:18:50.127 --> 00:18:52.565
flegt men oyfn veg gefinen a kartofl a alte,

00:18:52.565 --> 00:18:56.132
un a mol, eyn mol a vokh, flegt men dir ye a mol gebn a shtikl broyt.

00:18:56.627 --> 00:19:02.713
iz, eyn mol hot men undz arayngefirt in a dorf, a kleyne grupe, dos iz geven efsher tsvey hundert meydlekh,

00:19:03.242 --> 00:19:05.193
un di meydlekh

00:19:05.875 --> 00:19:07.930
hobn, hot der daytsh,

00:19:07.930 --> 00:19:11.260
vayle zey hobn dokh shoyn gelofn, zey hobn dokh shoyn, di daytshn hobn shoyn moyre gehat,

00:19:11.260 --> 00:19:13.800
a teyl fun zey hobn zikh ongeton undzere zakhn

00:19:14.093 --> 00:19:15.656
ven m'hot undz getribn.

00:19:16.675 --> 00:19:21.454
dos iz geven in yanuar, nayntsn finef un fertsik. di daytshn hobn shoyn farshpilt,

00:19:21.454 --> 00:19:23.160
zey hobn gevust az zey farshpiln.

00:19:23.982 --> 00:19:26.054
hot men undz arayngefirt in dem dorf.

00:19:26.054 --> 00:19:31.468
un in dem dorf hot men gezogt, oybe m'vet undz nisht gebn keyn kartofl tsu esn veln mir oyfraysn dem dorf.

00:19:32.318 --> 00:19:35.535
un in dem dorf, dos ershte vos ikh hob gezen,

00:19:35.592 --> 00:19:39.535
yidishe taleysim oyf di fentster, zey hobn es gemakht far gardin.

00:19:41.734 --> 00:19:45.558
un dos tsveyte, ven di daytshn hobn gefregt ver zaynen zey,

00:19:45.615 --> 00:19:48.768
hot men gezogt, dos zaynen prostitutkes un farbrekher.

00:19:48.768 --> 00:19:50.335
me firt zey fun turme.

00:19:51.606 --> 00:19:54.402
un ikh veys a bisl hob ikh zikh oryentirt,

00:19:54.402 --> 00:19:59.362
ikh hob gevust az s'iz geven dortn a rizike sotsyalistishe demokratishe partey far der milkhome,

00:19:59.706 --> 00:20:01.607
hob ikh gefregt a kashe:

00:20:01.900 --> 00:20:08.914
zog ikh, vu zaynen di sotsyalistn do? vu zaynen di daytshn? vo-, veysn zey nit az ikh bin nisht keyn prostitutke, ikh bin nisht keyn farbrekher?

00:20:08.937 --> 00:20:12.258
azelkhe kinder vi ikh zaynen geven zeyer a sakh in yener tsayt,

00:20:12.258 --> 00:20:13.608
di ale zaynen geven.

00:20:13.608 --> 00:20:20.557
ober azoy hot men zey gepashet, azoy hot men zey ertsoygn, azoy hot men zey gezogt, az mir zaynen di farbrekher, mir zaynen di prostitutkes.

00:20:21.441 --> 00:20:24.219
un fun dan on zaynen mir gegangen in

00:20:24.462 --> 00:20:25.860
in Ravensbrik,

00:20:27.642 --> 00:20:28.793
un in,

00:20:30.705 --> 00:20:34.546
fun Ravensbrik in Layptsik, un fun Layptsik

00:20:35.025 --> 00:20:38.205
in Malkhov, un fun Malkhov vayter oyfn veg.

00:20:38.205 --> 00:20:39.995
un bafrayt bin ikh gevorn oyfn veg.

00:20:40.392 --> 00:20:42.346
nor zayendik, ikh,

00:20:42.346 --> 00:20:45.785
zayendik in AUSCHWITZ hob ikh gefayert a geburtstog.

00:20:46.686 --> 00:20:48.722
ikh hob gearbet a nakht-shikht,

00:20:49.808 --> 00:20:54.070
ikh bin gekumen tsurik, iz gelegn a kaylekhdike shtikl broyt,

00:20:54.569 --> 00:20:55.538
shvartse,

00:20:56.085 --> 00:20:59.150
mit a bisl marmelade, royte,

00:20:59.190 --> 00:21:01.259
un s'iz gelegn a kleyn bikhele.

00:21:01.435 --> 00:21:04.719
der bikhele iz azoy groys vi mayn hant.

00:21:05.907 --> 00:21:08.932
ikh hob gegarbet mit zekhtsn meydlekh yidishe,

00:21:08.932 --> 00:21:11.688
un yedn meydl iz geven fun an ander land.

00:21:13.180 --> 00:21:21.544
s'iz geven fun frantsoyzishe meydlekh, un s'iz geven fun, afile yisroeldike meydlekh vos zey hobn tsufelik geven in EUROPE un zaynen farkhapt gevorn durkh di daytshn.

00:21:23.001 --> 00:21:27.011
in dem bikhele hobn zikh arayngeshribn ale zekhtsn meydlekh.

00:21:27.034 --> 00:21:29.992
un m'hot ongeshribn, "frayheyt, frayheyt, frayheyt."

00:21:29.992 --> 00:21:31.550
un in ale shprakhn.

00:21:31.725 --> 00:21:34.520
der bikhele gefint zikh haynt in Khurbn-

00:21:35.100 --> 00:21:36.731
MUSEUM in Montreol.

00:21:37.497 --> 00:21:38.908
un dos iz der,

00:21:39.319 --> 00:21:42.063
in der oysshtelung, dos iz der tshvok fun der oysshtelung.

00:21:43.900 --> 00:21:47.025
iz, ven ikh hob zikh g- umgekert dortn t-,

00:21:47.200 --> 00:21:48.594
der bikhele

00:21:49.275 --> 00:21:50.889
iz far mir geven

00:21:51.098 --> 00:21:57.066
lebn, az ikh in di, in yenem gehenem hobn mentshn getrakht vegn mir. in yenem gehenem

00:21:57.358 --> 00:21:58.702
hobn mentshn

00:21:58.742 --> 00:22:00.848
s-, der eyntsiker vuntsh vos iz geven,

00:22:00.848 --> 00:22:03.174
"frayheyt, frayheyt, frayheyt!"

00:22:03.838 --> 00:22:08.253
un ikh hob dem bikhele gebrakht mit zikh durkh, un biz haynt tsu tog,

00:22:08.479 --> 00:22:10.633
nisht hobndik keyn hor oyfn kop,

00:22:10.673 --> 00:22:12.641
nisht hobndik keyn kleyder,

00:22:12.850 --> 00:22:14.348
bloyz a kots

00:22:14.348 --> 00:22:16.775
mit a &lt;pasha&gt; vos ikh hob getrogn,

00:22:16.832 --> 00:22:22.192
veys ikh nisht vi azoy ikh hob bahaltn dem bikhele. ikh hob es geratevet, un ikh hob es gebrakht do.

00:22:24.200 --> 00:22:24.690
ye.

00:22:25.270 --> 00:22:27.103
un dos iz oykh fun dem gehenem.

00:22:28.324 --> 00:22:31.591
vu bistu geven nokh AUSCHWI- nokh der bafrayung?

00:22:31.362 --> 00:22:32.908
nokh der bafrayung

00:22:33.707 --> 00:22:35.540
bin ikh geven etlekhe...

00:22:35.428 --> 00:22:37.312
un ven bistu geven bafrayt?

00:22:36.863 --> 00:22:38.527
in nayntsn,

00:22:38.685 --> 00:22:40.096
finef un fertsik.

00:22:39.192 --> 00:22:42.189
finef un fertsik in dem dray un tsvantsiktn april.

00:22:42.516 --> 00:22:44.164
un vu bistu gegangen?

00:22:42.583 --> 00:22:43.370
ye.

00:22:44.035 --> 00:22:46.040
dos ershte vos ikh bin gegangen

00:22:46.040 --> 00:22:49.530
in shpitol arayn. mir hobn bafrayt gevorn untern frayen himl,

00:22:49.823 --> 00:22:51.954
un ven mir zaynen bafrayt gevorn,

00:22:51.954 --> 00:22:59.334
azoy di daytshn hobn tselofn un mir hobn oykh nisht gevust, m'hot undz gefirt durkh Drezdn, durkh di ale, durkh di a, durkh gants Daytshland, m'hot undz geshlept.

00:22:59.460 --> 00:23:01.230
du bist geven lebn a taykh, yo?

00:23:01.280 --> 00:23:02.979
ye, d- E- ELBA.

00:23:02.867 --> 00:23:03.806
ELBA.

00:23:03.323 --> 00:23:06.568
ye. der taykh ELBA, ye, dortn bin ikh bafrayt gevorn.

00:23:04.100 --> 00:23:04.790
ELBA.

00:23:06.568 --> 00:23:10.238
dortn iz geven a plats vu s'hobn zikh geey- geeynikt

00:23:10.238 --> 00:23:12.345
di rusn mit di amerikaner.

00:23:12.942 --> 00:23:14.305
zaynen mir

00:23:14.305 --> 00:23:16.294
ge- bafrayt gevorn durkh di rusn.

00:23:16.435 --> 00:23:21.207
ober mir zaynen geven zeyer oysgematert, hobn mir epes fir meydlekh zikh bahaltn

00:23:21.207 --> 00:23:22.622
unter a bret,

00:23:23.218 --> 00:23:26.755
un mir zaynen dortn gelegn, un in, far tog,

00:23:27.488 --> 00:23:30.519
m'hot bombardirt shreklekh, vayl s'iz geven lebn Drezdn.

00:23:30.559 --> 00:23:37.218
m'hot azoy bombardirt az ir shtelt zikh ni-, s'iz geven likhtik fun bombes, vos di ru- di amerikaner hobn, di englender

00:23:37.326 --> 00:23:39.125
un di rusn hobn gevorfn.

00:23:39.874 --> 00:23:40.934
iz

00:23:40.934 --> 00:23:43.429
hobn z- in der fri, mir hobn gegefnt di oygn.

00:23:43.806 --> 00:23:48.781
hot tsugegangen tsu undz a rus in tsivile kleyder un geredt tsu undz in r- in rusish,

00:23:48.781 --> 00:23:50.229
"meyd- kinder,

00:23:50.590 --> 00:23:54.499
ir zaynt bafrayt. geyt aroys fun dem, fun der lokh!"

00:23:55.483 --> 00:23:57.147
hob ikh im gefregt,

00:23:57.154 --> 00:24:01.485
"bist a emeser rus?" dos heys-, az ikh hob, vayl ikh hob gegert a bisl rusish, ob-, "bist a emeser rus?"

00:24:01.845 --> 00:24:08.625
zogt er, ye, vayl er hot ge- veyst dokh, der er- di ershte raye, di ershte linye fun di m-, zey hobn getro- zey hobn gev- oysgezen vi vilde.

00:24:08.625 --> 00:24:11.103
ober mir zaynen bafrayt gevorn fun zey.

00:24:11.110 --> 00:24:12.707
un zey zaynen avek,

00:24:12.848 --> 00:24:14.327
di rusn zaynen avek,

00:24:14.485 --> 00:24:20.351
zaynen mir zi-, hobn mir zikh tsugeshlept tsu a daytshishe hoyz, un mir zaynen shoyn geven a bisele zikher mit zikh hobn mir gebetn esn,

00:24:20.610 --> 00:24:23.628
un ven mir hobn genumen esn, mir hobn nisht gekent esn.

00:24:23.628 --> 00:24:25.380
mir zaynen geven ale,

00:24:25.487 --> 00:24:27.438
der kerper iz geven...

00:24:27.681 --> 00:24:31.744
s'iz shver zikh fortsushteln. mir hobn gegesn groz, mir hobn gegesn,

00:24:31.744 --> 00:24:35.454
eyne hot genumen esn shteynkoyln, hot zikh morg-, koyln, koyln vos men,

00:24:35.528 --> 00:24:42.204
hot zi oyf morgn geshtorbn, zi hot gekrign aza min far&lt;dreyen&gt; fun di kishkes un oyf morgn iz zi geshtorbn. hobn mir gevust az dos tor men nisht baysn.

00:24:42.312 --> 00:24:45.917
ober groz, un oyb men hot gefunen a kartofl, s'iz geven nokh dortn es-,

00:24:46.783 --> 00:24:53.729
fun letstn yor kartofl flegn mir, dos iz geven undzer esn. azoyernokh undzer, mir zaynen ale geven halb toyte.

00:24:53.972 --> 00:24:56.902
hot men genumen esn un dan iz men gevorn krank.

00:24:56.942 --> 00:24:59.419
mir hobn zikh gemuzt lernen vi tsu esn.

00:24:59.419 --> 00:25:00.395
farshteyst?

00:25:00.773 --> 00:25:03.332
zaynen mir tsugegangen, mir zaynen arayn in shpitol.

00:25:03.760 --> 00:25:06.336
frier zaynen mir geven oyfn veg un mir zaynen arayn,

00:25:06.426 --> 00:25:12.292
un mir hobn zikh gevolt geyn tsurik kedey tsu geyn keyn aheym. yeder eyner hot gekholemt tsu geyn aheym.

00:25:13.024 --> 00:25:15.633
iz, nokh etlekhe vokhn zayn in shpitol

00:25:16.416 --> 00:25:18.387
hobn mir zikh oysgelernt esn,

00:25:18.387 --> 00:25:19.971
un tsu undzer glik

00:25:21.495 --> 00:25:24.560
hobn mir getrofn a yidishn ofitser fun der rusisher armey.

00:25:26.187 --> 00:25:28.647
un er iz geven zeyer gut tsu undz.

00:25:28.647 --> 00:25:34.635
er hot gebrakht esn fun zayn militerishe dos, a yid, hot ge- er hot geven a hartsiker mentsh.

00:25:34.725 --> 00:25:37.419
un er hot avekgeshtelt a zelner me zol undz hitn.

00:25:37.476 --> 00:25:44.878
vayl di rusishe zelner hobn zikh oyfgefirt nit azoy fayn, di bafrayer undzere. zey hobn fargvaldikt. zey hobn geton vos zey hobn... zey zaynen geven vild &lt;demslt&gt;.

00:25:45.323 --> 00:25:52.894
zey hobn gedarft hobn froyen, hobn zey nisht gekukt tsi s'iz yidn, nisht-yidn, razirte, nisht-razirte, fun kontsentratsye-lagern. zey hobn genumen alem vos s'hot zikh gelozn.

00:25:53.288 --> 00:25:56.904
fun eyn yor biz nayntsik, alts iz geven gut. zaynen geven vild.

00:25:56.904 --> 00:26:01.719
hot der yid avekgeshtelt lebn undz a zelner, un m'hot undz opgehit. un mir zaynen geven a por vokhn,

00:26:01.810 --> 00:26:06.124
biz mir zaynen gekumen tsu zikh un er hot undz erleydikt a transport,

00:26:06.568 --> 00:26:09.366
a grupe vos iz farbaygegangen Poyln,

00:26:09.366 --> 00:26:11.087
heyst dos, a ban mit,

00:26:11.087 --> 00:26:15.050
un mir zaynen mit zey geforn efsher s'hot genumen fir vokhn mit dem ban.

00:26:15.124 --> 00:26:17.177
un di zelner hobn undz gegebn esn,

00:26:17.183 --> 00:26:19.016
un mir zaynen gekumen in Kroke.

00:26:19.039 --> 00:26:21.440
un fun Kroke zaynen mir geforn keyn Byalistok.

00:26:21.440 --> 00:26:24.601
dan iz shoyn geven yidishe komitetn ayngeordnt, dan iz shoyn geven

00:26:25.030 --> 00:26:26.475
a sakh zakhn.

00:26:27.190 --> 00:26:29.597
un du host khasene gehat in Byalistok, yo?

00:26:29.248 --> 00:26:30.030
NO.

00:26:30.030 --> 00:26:32.263
kh'hob nisht khasene gehat in Byalistok.

00:26:32.556 --> 00:26:34.642
ikh bin gekumen keyn,

00:26:35.982 --> 00:26:38.507
ikh bin geven in Byalistok zeks vokhn.

00:26:40.200 --> 00:26:45.273
in meshekh fun di zeks vokhn bin ikh eyn mol avekgeforn keyn Varshe vayl dortn iz geven a greserer,

00:26:45.718 --> 00:26:48.170
a groyse, a gresere tsol yidn.

00:26:48.170 --> 00:26:53.064
in Byalistok zaynen geven zeyer vintsik. Byalistoker, nisht geblibn, fun a shtot fun zekhtsik toyznt

00:26:53.064 --> 00:26:56.006
hobn zikh umgekert efsher tsen tsi tsvelef yidn.

00:26:56.535 --> 00:27:00.174
un ven ikh bin tsugegangen tsu mayn hoyz hot mir mayn struzh gezogt,

00:27:01.058 --> 00:27:02.244
"a, du lebst nokh?

00:27:02.244 --> 00:27:03.633
far vos lebstu?"

00:27:03.758 --> 00:27:06.975
farshtey-? er hot gevolt zayn der balebos un er iz gevorn der balebos.

00:27:07.673 --> 00:27:12.864
bin ikh avek in Varshe un dortn hob ikh bagegnt Faynern, er iz nokh geven a ofitser in der poylisher armey.

00:27:13.883 --> 00:27:19.445
un shpeter hot er gekumen keyn Byalistok un in meshekh fun dray khadoshim hobn mir khasene gehat beyde.

00:27:18.900 --> 00:27:19.918
vi heyst er?

00:27:19.890 --> 00:27:20.596
vos?

00:27:20.596 --> 00:27:21.842
Arn Fayner.

00:27:22.506 --> 00:27:23.515
mayn man.

00:27:23.515 --> 00:27:25.251
far nayn un fertsik yor.

00:27:25.122 --> 00:27:26.854
un ven hot ir khasene gehat?

00:27:26.623 --> 00:27:32.405
mir hobn khasene gehat in nayntsn zeks un fertsik, in AUGUST dem fir un tsvantsiktn.

00:27:33.863 --> 00:27:34.534
ye.

00:27:34.534 --> 00:27:38.480
vayl er hot zikh gedarft bafrayen fun militer, er hot nisht gevolt in mundir zayn a,

00:27:39.364 --> 00:27:44.994
khasene hobn, er hot moyre gehat. vos haynt-morgn ken er geharget vern. iz hot er gemakht zikher,

00:27:45.979 --> 00:27:50.613
hobn mir khasene gehat dem fer- dem fir un tsvantsiktn AUGUST, in nayntsn zeks un fertsik.

00:27:50.704 --> 00:27:52.352
un vu hot ir gevoynt?

00:27:52.088 --> 00:27:54.444
mir hobn gevoynt di ershte tsvey yor

00:27:54.670 --> 00:27:55.929
in Varshe.

00:27:56.391 --> 00:28:02.595
un mayn man hot gegarbet in Yidishn Tsentral-Komitet, un ikh hob oykh gegarbet in Yidishn Tsentral-Komitet, in an ander opteylung.

00:28:03.560 --> 00:28:04.636
un dernokh?

00:28:03.620 --> 00:28:04.080
ye.

00:28:04.529 --> 00:28:10.579
dernokh hobn mir bashlosn avek fun Poyln, vos vayter iz beser. mir hobn bikhlal nisht gevolt...

00:28:10.579 --> 00:28:12.450
zaynen mir avek in Shvedn.

00:28:13.114 --> 00:28:14.171
vi azoy?

00:28:14.245 --> 00:28:16.247
der Yidisher Arbeter-Komitet.

00:28:16.337 --> 00:28:20.094
azoy vi mayn man iz geven a aktiver sotsyalist far der milkhome,

00:28:20.100 --> 00:28:21.748
un a aktiver mentsh,

00:28:22.210 --> 00:28:23.841
iz a dank im

00:28:24.420 --> 00:28:27.603
hot d- de-, in Amerike,

00:28:27.846 --> 00:28:32.413
der Yidisher Arbeter hot ge- hot gegolfn, hot aroysgenumen firer fun der organizatsye.

00:28:32.487 --> 00:28:37.391
Arn Fayner iz geven ts- tsvishn di velkhe m'hot aroysgenumen un mir zaynen gekumen tsu forn in

00:28:37.431 --> 00:28:38.657
in Shvedn.

00:28:38.764 --> 00:28:42.099
ye. un in Shvedn hob ikh geborn mayn ershte kind.

00:28:41.650 --> 00:28:43.436
un dos iz in STOCKHOLM, yo?

00:28:43.422 --> 00:28:47.722
ye, gevoynt in STOCKHOLM, UNK, YES, mir hobn dortn gevoynt

00:28:47.722 --> 00:28:51.212
korev tsvey yor, un di shvedn zaynen geven oysergeveynlekh tsu undz.

00:28:51.488 --> 00:28:54.958
epes, der geyn dortn oyfn gas in Shvedn

00:28:56.044 --> 00:28:57.104
un nisht moy-

00:28:57.104 --> 00:29:01.506
farshteyst? in Poyln az mir hobn gegangen hobn mir zikh umgekukt keseyder

00:29:01.562 --> 00:29:06.736
tsi emetser geyt unter undz. bay nakht iz men geshlofn mit a revolver untern kop. di moyre

00:29:06.777 --> 00:29:08.323
az di polyakn

00:29:08.785 --> 00:29:12.019
veln nokh dir nokhkum- nisht genug s'iz geven,

00:29:14.607 --> 00:29:19.073
s'iz nisht genug geven vos s'iz geven di daytshn hobn mir undz geharget,

00:29:19.382 --> 00:29:22.700
ober ikh hob baygeven. a-, ikh bin a eydes.

00:29:22.842 --> 00:29:24.956
ven ikh hob zikh umgekert in Byalistok,

00:29:24.956 --> 00:29:25.974
ikh vil es nisht,

00:29:26.588 --> 00:29:31.205
ikh vil es nisht fargesn. ven ikh hob zikh umgekert in Byalistok hob ikh getrofn a bokher,

00:29:31.212 --> 00:29:33.062
fun eyn un tsvantsik yor.

00:29:33.169 --> 00:29:35.680
er hot ibergelebt di milkhome.
